{"word":"γραφίς","slug":"γραφίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γραφίς</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γράφω'><el>γράφω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a stile for writing</i> on waxen tablets, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <i>a needle for embroidering</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>embroidery</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}